<td bgcolor="#EEEEEE" colspan=2 class=news>
<table><tr><td valign=top><img src='images/icon_general.gif' alt='General News' border=0></td><td width="100%" valign=top>As promised yesterday..........<br><br><span class=quote>"The latest game to evolve from the brain of Tom Clancy is <A HREF="http://www.ghostrecon.com/" target=_new>Ghost Recon</A>. Based on the popular Rainbow 6 series you will journey through 15 huge, single player maps, as well as joining in with up to 36 people in on-line play. The demo includes a map that will not be in the final version of the game – although it can be imported - and is a prequel to the main storyline. Also included is basic multiplayer support. You can download the demo via a Gigex connection at the sites <A HREF="http://www.ghostrecon.com/demo.php" target=_new>demo download page</A>. There is also a list of mirrors <A HREF="http://www.ghostrecon.com/demo2.php" target=_new>over here</A>."</span><br><br>You can download the 76 meg file from the barrysworld ftp <A HREF="ftp://ftp.barrysworld.com/pub/games/othergames/demos/ghostrecondemo.exe" target=_new>here</A>.<br><br>[Taken from <A HREF="http://www.barrysworld.com/news/default.asp" target=_new>BarrysWorld</A> ]</td></tr></table>
