<td bgcolor="#EEEEEE" colspan=2 class=news>
<table><tr><td valign=top><img src='images/icon_general.gif' alt='General News' border=0></td><td width="100%" valign=top>I've just recieved words that an upcomming Sc-Fi Realism mod is in need of some modelers and animators.  Here's the scoop:<br><br><span class=quote>"There is an upcoming sci-fi special ops mod on the horizon.  It's called Section 9, and draws heavy influence from the Ghost in the Shell universe.<br><br>The main points of interest will be: Realistic bullet physics (penetration and ricochets based on bullet power and material), extremely advanced enemy (and friendly AI), and multiple branching paths through the game."</span><br><br>So, if you're a modeler, animator or 2D artist, give <A HREF="mailto:cruise@wytedragon.com">Cruise</A> a mail.  And say Buda sent you.<br><br></td></tr></table>
